1
00:01:05,728 --> 00:01:08,352
=No Doubt In Us=
(Adapted from the Manman comic No Doubt in Us)

2
00:01:08,352 --> 00:01:11,328
=Episode 8=

3
00:01:22,480 --> 00:01:23,239
Does it hurt?

4
00:01:24,599 --> 00:01:25,120
No.

5
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:26,920
I just feel sorry.

6
00:01:27,319 --> 00:01:28,079
I broke my word.

7
00:01:28,519 --> 00:01:29,719
Your body got hurt again.

8
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:32,480
I had way worse injuries

9
00:01:32,480 --> 00:01:33,760
from martial training before.

10
00:01:34,079 --> 00:01:35,159
I'm just worried...

11
00:01:37,879 --> 00:01:38,680
I'm fine.

12
00:01:39,359 --> 00:01:40,719
It's just that Lady Tao

13
00:01:40,920 --> 00:01:43,040
is so loyal to the one behind her.

14
00:01:43,599 --> 00:01:44,439
Actually,

15
00:01:44,640 --> 00:01:46,319
the person who killed her child

16
00:01:47,040 --> 00:01:48,519
was the child's own father.

17
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:50,040
What?

18
00:01:50,480 --> 00:01:51,200
Your Majesty!

19
00:01:52,079 --> 00:01:53,519
She's been having an affair

20
00:01:53,519 --> 00:01:55,519
with someone else for so long!

21
00:01:56,640 --> 00:01:57,840
How pitiful you are!

22
00:01:59,079 --> 00:02:00,040
Don't be upset!

23
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:01,239
Don't be...

24
00:02:05,319 --> 00:02:06,400
I'm not upset.

25
00:02:07,920 --> 00:02:08,879
Good that you're not.

26
00:02:10,319 --> 00:02:11,039
Xu Yu.

27
00:02:12,319 --> 00:02:13,759
I actually want to tell you.

28
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:15,479
All these years,

29
00:02:16,280 --> 00:02:19,199
I have never been intimate
with anyone in the harem.

30
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:34,520
Xu Yu!

31
00:02:39,800 --> 00:02:41,360
It was Lady Tao.

32
00:02:41,599 --> 00:02:42,879
She drugged me

33
00:02:43,159 --> 00:02:45,639
to make it look like
I'd shared a bed with her.

34
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:48,199
But my spies discovered this long ago.

35
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:49,719
We drugged her unconscious,

36
00:02:49,960 --> 00:02:50,919
making her believe

37
00:02:51,639 --> 00:02:53,000
that I had fallen into their trap.

38
00:02:54,080 --> 00:02:55,080
If that's the case,

39
00:02:55,159 --> 00:02:56,560
why didn't Your Majesty expose her?

40
00:02:56,759 --> 00:02:58,479
I want them to believe

41
00:02:59,200 --> 00:03:01,599
that I'm an easily manipulated Emperor.

42
00:03:02,159 --> 00:03:03,000
This way,

43
00:03:03,120 --> 00:03:04,680
they can brazenly

44
00:03:04,680 --> 00:03:06,439
reveal their true colors.

45
00:03:06,919 --> 00:03:08,960
Once the frontier war subsides,

46
00:03:09,719 --> 00:03:11,560
what I will resolve next

47
00:03:12,039 --> 00:03:14,039
is those traitorous rebels.

48
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:17,159
My family and the frontier soldiers

49
00:03:17,479 --> 00:03:19,199
will fully assist Your Majesty.

50
00:03:22,120 --> 00:03:22,639
Great.

51
00:03:25,520 --> 00:03:26,159
Your Majesty,

52
00:03:26,400 --> 00:03:28,919
so who is the one having
an affair with Lady Tao?

53
00:03:30,560 --> 00:03:31,560
No concrete evidence yet.

54
00:03:32,199 --> 00:03:33,039
But no rush.

55
00:03:33,639 --> 00:03:35,439
He'll surface eventually.

56
00:03:44,520 --> 00:03:46,240
Is there anything else you want to know?

57
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:47,800
I will tell you everything.

58
00:03:51,319 --> 00:03:52,240
Your Majesty,

59
00:03:52,680 --> 00:03:55,599
why are you unwilling to favor
the consorts in the harem?

60
00:03:55,879 --> 00:03:57,199
Is it because...

61
00:03:57,199 --> 00:03:58,199
Because...?

62
00:03:58,439 --> 00:04:00,599
Because, in my heart,

63
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:03,800
I only have one wife.

64
00:04:04,439 --> 00:04:05,360
And I only want

65
00:04:06,759 --> 00:04:07,800
that person.

66
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:15,639
Your Majesty.

67
00:04:15,719 --> 00:04:16,560
Your Majesty.

68
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:19,199
Prince Xiaoyao
and the Grand Preceptor are here.

69
00:04:19,639 --> 00:04:20,399
So late?

70
00:04:20,720 --> 00:04:21,720
It must be urgent.

71
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:23,079
Summon them.

72
00:04:24,959 --> 00:04:25,600
Well...

73
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:27,000
Summon them!

74
00:04:27,648 --> 00:04:28,160
Yes.

75
00:04:32,576 --> 00:04:33,079
Jinyun.

76
00:04:33,920 --> 00:04:34,800
You two.

77
00:04:34,839 --> 00:04:35,680
Where have you been?

78
00:04:36,600 --> 00:04:38,560
Why are you both soaking wet?

79
00:04:38,560 --> 00:04:39,072
Jinyun.

80
00:04:39,720 --> 00:04:41,759
We made a major discovery
in Fengyi Palace's lake.

81
00:04:49,160 --> 00:04:50,399
It's just a cloth doll.

82
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:53,319
This object

83
00:04:53,680 --> 00:04:55,160
is related to Dada witchcraft.

84
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:00,439
Your Majesty.

85
00:05:00,960 --> 00:05:01,519
Your Majesty.

86
00:05:02,279 --> 00:05:03,240
This meteorite iron

87
00:05:03,519 --> 00:05:05,519
is the key item for the soul swap.

88
00:05:12,959 --> 00:05:14,399
You must be overwhelmed with duties

89
00:05:14,399 --> 00:05:15,240
and misspoke.

90
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:17,000
What soul swap?

91
00:05:20,439 --> 00:05:21,639
Jinyun.

92
00:05:22,279 --> 00:05:23,600
You don't need to hide it.

93
00:05:23,959 --> 00:05:25,680
I guessed long ago
that you swapped bodies.

94
00:05:25,879 --> 00:05:26,879
"Long ago?"

95
00:05:26,879 --> 00:05:28,160
When did you find out?

96
00:05:29,319 --> 00:05:30,079
You told him?

97
00:05:31,720 --> 00:05:33,480
The prince did sound me out,

98
00:05:34,800 --> 00:05:36,160
but I didn't say a single word.

99
00:05:36,279 --> 00:05:37,199
I guessed it myself.

100
00:05:37,760 --> 00:05:38,304
Enough.

101
00:05:39,560 --> 00:05:40,600
Back to the cloth doll.

102
00:05:41,360 --> 00:05:44,000
This fell into the water along
with your meteorite iron sword.

103
00:05:44,199 --> 00:05:45,040
One large, one small.

104
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:46,360
One yin, one yang.

105
00:05:46,920 --> 00:05:48,319
The two opposites.

106
00:05:49,759 --> 00:05:50,720
(And the lightning)

107
00:05:50,720 --> 00:05:51,759
(carried electricity.)

108
00:05:53,319 --> 00:05:54,600
(When you two)

109
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:56,560
(were in the middle of the two poles,)

110
00:05:56,800 --> 00:05:58,160
(the lightning passed through.)

111
00:05:58,839 --> 00:05:59,639
(Therefore,)

112
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:01,480
(your souls swapped.)

113
00:06:04,240 --> 00:06:05,560
This was given by Zhao Qiluo.

114
00:06:05,839 --> 00:06:07,079
She got the Empress's Seal,

115
00:06:07,439 --> 00:06:09,720
took many consorts
to the Xuantian Temple outside,

116
00:06:10,439 --> 00:06:11,160
and came back

117
00:06:11,160 --> 00:06:12,079
with this,

118
00:06:12,360 --> 00:06:14,199
calling it a blessing for the consorts.

119
00:06:14,528 --> 00:06:15,079
I thought,

120
00:06:15,079 --> 00:06:16,040
"This ugly doll

121
00:06:16,040 --> 00:06:17,680
needs to be put on the bed to work?"

122
00:06:17,759 --> 00:06:19,200
So I ordered someone to discard it.

123
00:06:19,560 --> 00:06:21,519
Could someone
have thrown it into the lake,

124
00:06:21,519 --> 00:06:22,720
and that made it work?

125
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:24,920
There are two
of these dolls: yin and yang.

126
00:06:25,439 --> 00:06:27,439
If placed under a bed for long,

127
00:06:27,720 --> 00:06:29,240
it weakens the people physically.

128
00:06:29,879 --> 00:06:31,120
If yin and yang unite,

129
00:06:31,399 --> 00:06:33,279
it causes Your Majesty
to fall into a coma

130
00:06:34,399 --> 00:06:35,560
and die during intercourse.

131
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:39,160
Zhao Qiluo.

132
00:06:39,639 --> 00:06:41,160
How dare she use such an evil thing

133
00:06:41,360 --> 00:06:42,600
against me!

134
00:06:43,879 --> 00:06:46,688
The Marchioness of Zhenbei
lives at Xuantian Temple for long.

135
00:06:47,040 --> 00:06:48,120
I suspect this matter

136
00:06:48,759 --> 00:06:50,480
is linked to Marquis of Zhenbei again.

137
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:52,600
Dada sorcery has entered the palace.

138
00:06:53,319 --> 00:06:54,680
I should have noticed it.

139
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:56,000
To reverse this,

140
00:06:56,439 --> 00:06:58,160
Your Majesty must find the other doll.

141
00:07:12,439 --> 00:07:13,759
Surround the room!

142
00:07:13,959 --> 00:07:15,480
No fly escapes.

143
00:07:16,279 --> 00:07:17,360
Your Majesty,

144
00:07:18,040 --> 00:07:19,279
what are you doing?

145
00:07:19,879 --> 00:07:21,439
You persecuted Lady Tao,

146
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:24,399
and now, you seek to persecute me?

147
00:07:25,279 --> 00:07:25,959
Under the bed.

148
00:07:26,199 --> 00:07:26,800
Search.

149
00:07:26,800 --> 00:07:27,360
Yes.

150
00:07:30,480 --> 00:07:31,560
What are you searching for?

151
00:07:31,879 --> 00:07:33,079
Who authorized this search?

152
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:35,800
Your Majesty.

153
00:07:45,079 --> 00:07:47,240
Come with me to see the Empress Dowager.

154
00:07:47,240 --> 00:07:48,279
Consort Zhao.

155
00:07:51,079 --> 00:07:51,879
Mother.

156
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:53,519
Consort Zhao.

157
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:56,800
Uncle won't tolerate such mischief.

158
00:07:57,319 --> 00:07:58,079
But

159
00:07:58,079 --> 00:07:59,639
this is truly sinister.

160
00:07:59,959 --> 00:08:01,160
It is Dada sorcery.

161
00:08:01,360 --> 00:08:02,199
The Grand Preceptor

162
00:08:02,360 --> 00:08:03,240
said it would cause me

163
00:08:04,160 --> 00:08:05,240
to die

164
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:06,720
from illness in months.

165
00:08:07,720 --> 00:08:08,839
Dada sorcery.

166
00:08:09,120 --> 00:08:10,560
How dare she!

167
00:08:11,160 --> 00:08:13,000
This is banned
yet persists in the palace.

168
00:08:13,199 --> 00:08:14,160
I am certain

169
00:08:14,319 --> 00:08:16,120
that court officials

170
00:08:16,120 --> 00:08:17,160
are behind this.

171
00:08:17,920 --> 00:08:18,600
I'm afraid

172
00:08:19,160 --> 00:08:20,560
Uncle is implicated too.

173
00:08:26,199 --> 00:08:27,560
Any member of our Zhao family

174
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:29,480
who is disloyal to you,

175
00:08:29,959 --> 00:08:31,800
I'll execute them personally.

176
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:33,159
Harem affairs

177
00:08:33,480 --> 00:08:35,039
mirror court politics.

178
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:37,600
This involves the consort
and the Zhao family.

179
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:39,279
The judgment

180
00:08:39,759 --> 00:08:41,200
is yours to make, Mother.

181
00:08:41,600 --> 00:08:42,279
Alright.

182
00:08:49,320 --> 00:08:50,960
Greetings, Mother.

183
00:08:50,960 --> 00:08:51,799
Your Majesty.

184
00:08:57,320 --> 00:09:00,200
This was found in Consort Zhao's room.

185
00:09:00,519 --> 00:09:02,000
Please examine it.

186
00:09:13,519 --> 00:09:14,600
Zhao Qiluo,

187
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:15,960
what were you plotting?

188
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:17,720
Using sorcery against His Majesty?

189
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:20,799
I'd never do that!

190
00:09:21,799 --> 00:09:22,919
It must be you

191
00:09:24,919 --> 00:09:26,600
who are spreading lies to frame me!

192
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:28,320
How dare you

193
00:09:28,320 --> 00:09:29,879
slander the Empress now?

194
00:09:30,399 --> 00:09:31,240
Answer me.

195
00:09:31,519 --> 00:09:32,879
Where did these dolls

196
00:09:33,120 --> 00:09:34,240
come from?

197
00:09:35,840 --> 00:09:36,559
Tell me!

198
00:09:38,440 --> 00:09:39,200
Aunt,

199
00:09:40,159 --> 00:09:41,240
I know

200
00:09:41,240 --> 00:09:43,639
Dada sorcery is forbidden in the palace.

201
00:09:44,279 --> 00:09:45,279
But I

202
00:09:46,480 --> 00:09:47,519
only used

203
00:09:47,759 --> 00:09:49,600
this forbidden sorcery

204
00:09:49,600 --> 00:09:51,440
to bear a royal heir.

205
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:54,440
Your Majesty.

206
00:09:55,639 --> 00:09:56,879
I entered the palace years ago.

207
00:09:57,279 --> 00:09:59,399
You know my heart.

208
00:10:00,600 --> 00:10:01,960
But you always...

209
00:10:03,799 --> 00:10:04,480
Mother.

210
00:10:05,039 --> 00:10:07,720
It seems Consort Zhao
truly knew nothing.

211
00:10:10,559 --> 00:10:11,639
You believe me!

212
00:10:11,720 --> 00:10:13,240
I know

213
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:15,440
you conspired with Lady Tao

214
00:10:16,000 --> 00:10:18,360
to obtain my blood for your curse.

215
00:10:18,799 --> 00:10:20,519
But you didn't realize

216
00:10:20,519 --> 00:10:21,960
she was using you all along.

217
00:10:31,799 --> 00:10:33,480
So she plotted against me?

218
00:10:33,840 --> 00:10:34,600
Aunt,

219
00:10:34,679 --> 00:10:35,519
I got these dolls

220
00:10:35,519 --> 00:10:37,679
with Lady Tao at the Xuantian Temple.

221
00:10:38,519 --> 00:10:40,240
She said they were used for fertility,

222
00:10:40,440 --> 00:10:42,200
insisting I must get them.

223
00:10:43,360 --> 00:10:44,000
Guards.

224
00:10:44,320 --> 00:10:45,399
Summon Lady Tao.

225
00:10:45,664 --> 00:10:48,480
(Ci'an Palace)

226
00:10:49,519 --> 00:10:50,840
Did you take the consort

227
00:10:50,919 --> 00:10:52,480
to the Xuantian Temple

228
00:10:52,480 --> 00:10:54,360
and bring back these two dolls?

229
00:10:55,240 --> 00:10:56,639
Yes,

230
00:10:56,879 --> 00:10:59,120
I took Her Highness
to the Xuantian Temple.

231
00:10:59,120 --> 00:11:00,240
You admit it?

232
00:11:00,840 --> 00:11:01,399
Yes.

233
00:11:01,720 --> 00:11:02,360
How dare you!

234
00:11:02,799 --> 00:11:04,600
Using sorcery against His Majesty?

235
00:11:05,360 --> 00:11:06,440
I didn't.

236
00:11:07,919 --> 00:11:09,240
The evidence is irrefutable.

237
00:11:09,480 --> 00:11:10,480
How dare you deny it?

238
00:11:12,120 --> 00:11:12,960
Lady Tao.

239
00:11:13,279 --> 00:11:14,440
Look closely.

240
00:11:14,720 --> 00:11:16,320
These are Dada words.

241
00:11:16,639 --> 00:11:17,960
This is Dada sorcery.

242
00:11:18,720 --> 00:11:20,360
Confess truthfully,

243
00:11:20,799 --> 00:11:22,080
and I may spare your life.

244
00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:29,879
I...

245
00:11:33,039 --> 00:11:34,159
I have nothing to say.

246
00:11:38,882 --> 00:11:40,799
(Her uncle Tao Kan,
Marquis of Zhenbei, is behind this.)

247
00:11:40,799 --> 00:11:41,639
So this means

248
00:11:42,039 --> 00:11:43,159
the Marquis of Zhenbei

249
00:11:43,639 --> 00:11:45,039
colludes with Dada?

250
00:11:45,279 --> 00:11:47,000
A Dada sorcerer disguised as a priest

251
00:11:47,320 --> 00:11:50,080
met secretly with the marchioness
of Zhenbei at the Xuantian Temple.

252
00:11:50,639 --> 00:11:51,879
I witnessed it clearly.

253
00:11:52,159 --> 00:11:53,279
After Lady Tao's exposure,

254
00:11:53,879 --> 00:11:55,240
her father and brothers

255
00:11:55,240 --> 00:11:56,480
were impeached and exiled.

256
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:58,759
They'll likely never
see each other again.

257
00:11:59,039 --> 00:12:00,720
They're openly challenging us now.

258
00:12:00,840 --> 00:12:02,000
This is just too brazen.

259
00:12:06,120 --> 00:12:06,960
No matter what,

260
00:12:07,360 --> 00:12:09,639
if we are united, we fear no one.

261
00:12:16,360 --> 00:12:19,480
I'm so jealous of your relationship.

262
00:12:20,720 --> 00:12:21,600
You may leave.

263
00:12:22,600 --> 00:12:23,159
Go.

264
00:12:30,000 --> 00:12:32,639
Though hateful, Lady Tao is pitiable.

265
00:12:33,200 --> 00:12:35,679
Her entire life was manipulated.

266
00:12:36,600 --> 00:12:37,200
What?

267
00:12:37,960 --> 00:12:39,120
Feeling sympathy?

268
00:12:40,679 --> 00:12:41,360
No.

269
00:12:42,080 --> 00:12:45,000
Hearing her siblings
suffer for her crimes,

270
00:12:46,240 --> 00:12:48,679
I suddenly miss my father and brothers.

271
00:12:49,759 --> 00:12:51,519
(Xu Yu and her father)

272
00:12:51,519 --> 00:12:53,240
(haven't seen each other
for a long time.)

273
00:12:55,320 --> 00:12:56,000
Xu Yu,

274
00:12:57,000 --> 00:12:58,440
shall I send a letter home for you?

275
00:12:58,759 --> 00:12:59,519
No need.

276
00:13:00,039 --> 00:13:01,279
War dispatches take priority.

277
00:13:01,279 --> 00:13:02,639
No need to trouble.

278
00:13:10,840 --> 00:13:12,039
With a wife like you,

279
00:13:13,080 --> 00:13:14,000
how could my empire

280
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:16,360
not be secure?

281
00:13:18,879 --> 00:13:20,240
You flatter me too much.

282
00:13:46,360 --> 00:13:47,080
Your Majesty!

283
00:13:47,639 --> 00:13:48,879
By my count,

284
00:13:49,320 --> 00:13:50,919
it shouldn't be time yet.

285
00:13:51,039 --> 00:13:51,840
Xu Yu,

286
00:13:53,120 --> 00:13:55,639
do you have some unfound health issue?

287
00:13:56,480 --> 00:13:57,399
No.

288
00:13:57,799 --> 00:13:58,559
Someone!

289
00:14:01,039 --> 00:14:01,888
Summon Jiang Tang!

290
00:14:02,000 --> 00:14:02,519
Quickly!

291
00:14:02,759 --> 00:14:03,720
Summon Jiang Tang!

292
00:14:04,039 --> 00:14:04,720
Yes!

293
00:14:06,480 --> 00:14:07,279
Your Majesty.

294
00:14:19,759 --> 00:14:20,600
I'm afraid

295
00:14:21,120 --> 00:14:22,600
it's not a cold womb syndrome

296
00:14:22,840 --> 00:14:23,879
troubling the Empress.

297
00:14:24,279 --> 00:14:25,200
It indicates poisoning.

298
00:14:25,519 --> 00:14:26,399
Poisoning?

299
00:14:28,279 --> 00:14:29,919
Someone means you harm?

300
00:14:30,240 --> 00:14:30,960
I...

301
00:14:31,519 --> 00:14:33,240
This poison isn't lethal,

302
00:14:33,240 --> 00:14:34,320
but bad for her health.

303
00:14:34,600 --> 00:14:35,679
If prolonged,

304
00:14:36,480 --> 00:14:37,840
conceiving may become impossible.

305
00:14:37,840 --> 00:14:38,720
- What?
- What?

306
00:14:40,320 --> 00:14:42,600
I must find out who did this.

307
00:14:51,120 --> 00:14:51,799
Your Majesty.

308
00:14:52,200 --> 00:14:52,799
Your Majesty.

309
00:14:53,159 --> 00:14:54,759
If I am not mistaken,

310
00:14:55,120 --> 00:14:55,919
the poison

311
00:14:57,360 --> 00:14:58,320
is in this incense.

312
00:15:07,168 --> 00:15:07,720
Investigate.

313
00:15:08,000 --> 00:15:08,720
Don't.

314
00:15:09,399 --> 00:15:10,279
Why?

315
00:15:11,919 --> 00:15:12,720
Jiang Tang.

316
00:15:14,919 --> 00:15:15,919
You may leave now.

317
00:15:22,799 --> 00:15:23,519
Xu Yu,

318
00:15:23,919 --> 00:15:24,759
