319
00:15:25,240 --> 00:15:26,279
They mean you harm.

320
00:15:31,559 --> 00:15:32,600
Why are you crying?

321
00:15:35,919 --> 00:15:36,879
Xiao Jinyun.

322
00:15:42,360 --> 00:15:44,240
Have you truly never regretted

323
00:15:45,639 --> 00:15:46,919
choosing me as your Empress?

324
00:15:48,080 --> 00:15:49,720
I have only you as my Empress.

325
00:15:50,320 --> 00:15:51,440
No one could replace you.

326
00:15:59,960 --> 00:16:00,840
I believe

327
00:16:01,360 --> 00:16:03,039
you still carry

328
00:16:04,679 --> 00:16:06,039
some youthful affection for me,

329
00:16:07,480 --> 00:16:09,399
but compared to your imperial power,

330
00:16:10,320 --> 00:16:12,159
that affection means nothing.

331
00:16:13,960 --> 00:16:14,840
Xu Yu,

332
00:16:15,519 --> 00:16:16,799
what are you saying?

333
00:16:22,559 --> 00:16:23,639
Xiao Jinyun.

334
00:16:25,879 --> 00:16:26,799
This incense burner

335
00:16:27,399 --> 00:16:29,840
was gifted to me by the Empress Dowager
at our royal wedding.

336
00:16:30,799 --> 00:16:32,639
It concerns the heir and the court.

337
00:16:33,919 --> 00:16:36,080
How could you know nothing about it?

338
00:16:54,848 --> 00:16:59,932
♪Parting clouds
to pluck the waxing moon♪

339
00:17:00,768 --> 00:17:05,120
♪Brewing a pot of bygone years♪

340
00:17:06,560 --> 00:17:11,681
♪Chill flame, window shade,
console my grieving soul♪

341
00:17:12,352 --> 00:17:16,896
♪Drunk through lifetimes
with no dreams returned♪

342
00:17:17,568 --> 00:17:22,981
♪If not for letting go, how could I
bear to shatter this dream♪

343
00:17:23,296 --> 00:17:28,928
♪Returning to drift
through the mortal world♪

344
00:17:29,216 --> 00:17:31,462
♪Like her, like me, like you♪

345
00:17:31,462 --> 00:17:35,456
♪Hairpins carved
with endless sighs and regrets♪

346
00:17:35,808 --> 00:17:40,633
♪Fate laid bare my deepest thoughts♪

347
00:17:40,928 --> 00:17:43,136
♪Like vows, like remorse, like love♪

348
00:17:43,136 --> 00:17:46,912
♪Loving, hurting,
and regretting our late meeting♪

349
00:17:46,912 --> 00:17:52,032
♪Tell me, after all this entanglement,
who regrets it more♪
